Questions to calibrate your preferences

- Option C: You take Stone in exchange for Pencil+Apple+Quill. This is a more aggressive concession on my side to move Stone to you if your valuation of Stone is very high relative to those three items.
- Option D (if you want to stay balanced): Stone stays with me; I offer Pencil + Apple to you now, and we split Jewel + Quill in Round 3. This is a more incremental, low-friction path.

Your turn
